                "CHSEP",
                "GSPEC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " A thick-target production",
                "rate curve was measured for 88Y produced in the",
                "proton bombardment of SrCl2 target.",
                "Activations were performed using degraders of various",
                "thicknesses to cover the energy region from threshold",
                "up to 17.5 MeV energy at the ATOMKI cyclotron in",
                "Debrecen, Hungary.",
                "Targets were irradiated inside the cyclotron vacuum",
                "at an average beam current of 50 nA, each bombardment",
                "lasting about 30 min."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "MONITOR": [
            {
